WEBVTT

00:00.868 --> 00:03.871
<b>[upbeat music]</b>

00:03.871 --> 00:11.745
<b>♪</b>

00:11.745 --> 00:14.281
<b>- The key to the perfect</b>
<b>anniversary present for</b>

00:14.281 --> 00:16.583
<b>your parents is simple,</b>
<b>know your audience.</b>

00:16.583 --> 00:19.253
<b>And since my folks love</b>
<b>what I bring to the table,</b>

00:19.253 --> 00:21.655
<b>I make them the same thing</b>
<b>every year:</b>

00:21.655 --> 00:24.558
<b>this awesome coffee mug!</b>

00:24.558 --> 00:25.559
<b>- Coffee mug?</b>

00:25.559 --> 00:27.261
<b>I thought it was</b>
<b>a paperweight.</b>

00:27.261 --> 00:29.930
<b>- Paperweight? That thing is</b>
<b>definitely a pencil holder.</b>

00:29.930 --> 00:31.598
<b>- Negatory.</b>

00:31.598 --> 00:34.334
<b>Clearly it's a bust of German</b>
<b>philosopher Immanuel Kant.</b>

00:34.334 --> 00:36.570
<b>- I "Kant" even tell</b>
<b>what it is.</b>

00:36.570 --> 00:37.905
<b>[laughs]</b>

00:37.905 --> 00:40.007
<b>- Clearly no one can figure out</b>
<b>what that thing is.</b>

00:40.007 --> 00:41.275
<b>No wonder Mom and Dad just</b>

00:41.275 --> 00:42.876
<b>throw all your old gifts</b>
<b>in the attic.</b>

00:42.876 --> 00:44.378
<b>all: [gasp]</b>
<b>- What?</b>

00:44.378 --> 00:46.580
<b>Lola must've been</b>
<b>messing around with me.</b>

00:46.580 --> 00:48.815
<b>Mom and Dad love</b>
<b>my paperweights.</b>

00:48.815 --> 00:50.384
<b>I mean, coffee mugs!</b>

00:50.384 --> 00:52.252
<b>What's this?</b>

00:52.252 --> 00:54.955
<b>Do not open. Okay.</b>

00:54.955 --> 00:57.491
<b>[gasps]</b>
<b>It's true.</b>

00:57.491 --> 01:00.060
<b>Mom and Dad do hate my gifts!</b>

01:00.060 --> 01:02.396
<b>- If you turn your head</b>
<b>to the side and squint,</b>

01:02.396 --> 01:04.665
<b>it almost looks like</b>
<b>Aunt Shirley.</b>

01:04.665 --> 01:06.066
<b> <i>[scream]</i> </b>

01:06.066 --> 01:07.434
<b>- Or an inflamed liver.</b>

01:07.434 --> 01:08.902
<b>- When he's this pathetic,</b>

01:08.902 --> 01:11.104
<b>it takes all the joy out of</b>
<b>making fun of him.</b>

01:11.104 --> 01:12.940
<b>- I can hear you!</b>

01:12.940 --> 01:14.775
<b>together: We know!</b>

01:14.775 --> 01:16.910
<b>- Mom and Dad's anniversary is</b>
<b>tomorrow.</b>

01:16.910 --> 01:19.813
<b>What am I gonna do?</b>

01:21.882 --> 01:23.350
<b>[camera shutter clicks]</b>

01:23.350 --> 01:25.986
<b>- Oh, I think</b>
<b>an idea's developing.</b>

01:25.986 --> 01:27.788
<b>Aah!</b>

01:27.788 --> 01:30.691
<b>I've figured out the perfect</b>
<b>present for Mom and Dad!</b>

01:30.691 --> 01:31.992
<b>Ta-da!</b>

01:31.992 --> 01:33.527
<b>- You're giving them</b>
<b>Dad's old camera?</b>

01:33.527 --> 01:35.796
<b>- Wow, you are cheap.</b>

01:35.796 --> 01:39.099
<b>- No, not the camera!</b>
<b>A photograph of all of us!</b>

01:39.099 --> 01:42.102
<b>- Why use that old thing when</b>
<b>you can just use a cell phone?</b>

01:42.102 --> 01:43.303
<b>- Because that would be like</b>

01:43.303 --> 01:45.572
<b>painting the "Mona Lisa"</b>
<b>with a crayon.</b>

01:45.572 --> 01:48.141
<b>- Wow, this may be the year</b>
<b>you don't fail miserably</b>

01:48.141 --> 01:49.610
<b>and crush</b>
<b>Mom and Dad's souls.</b>

01:49.610 --> 01:52.112
<b>- Thank you for</b>
<b>the vote of confidence.</b>

01:52.112 --> 01:55.382
<b>Everyone to the backyard!</b>

01:55.382 --> 01:57.150
<b>Okay, that's it.</b>

01:57.150 --> 01:58.619
<b>Leni, scooch to the left.</b>

01:58.619 --> 02:00.420
<b>- Your other left.</b>
<b>- [giggles]</b>

02:00.420 --> 02:02.890
<b>- Perfect.</b>
<b>Someone grab Lily.</b>

02:02.890 --> 02:04.892
<b>Thank you. Good.</b>

02:04.892 --> 02:06.960
<b>Just gotta set the timer and...</b>

02:06.960 --> 02:08.829
<b>everybody say cheese!</b>

02:08.829 --> 02:10.797
<b>all: Chee...</b>

02:10.797 --> 02:13.700
<b>- When is it gonna flash?</b>
<b>My jaw is cramping up!</b>

02:13.700 --> 02:14.868
<b>all: eeeeee...</b>

02:14.868 --> 02:16.703
<b>- Give it a second.</b>
<b>all: eeeee...</b>

02:16.703 --> 02:19.273
<b>- Yeah, I knew he'd blow it.</b>
<b>Let's do selfies instead.</b>

02:19.273 --> 02:20.974
<b>- Totes!</b>
<b>- No, wait--Doi!</b>

02:20.974 --> 02:23.510
<b>- I "nose" just what this</b>
<b>picture needs!</b>

02:23.510 --> 02:24.912
<b>[laughs]</b>

02:24.912 --> 02:26.313
<b>- Come on, Luan, you can't</b>
<b>wear those in the photo.</b>

02:26.313 --> 02:28.549
<b>- Oh, don't be such a Groucho!</b>
<b>[laughs]</b>

02:28.549 --> 02:30.851
<b>- What this photo needs</b>
<b>are some tunes!</b>

02:30.851 --> 02:33.887
<b>- No, no, no, no, no,</b>
<b>photographs don't have--</b>

02:33.887 --> 02:35.322
<b>[loud chord]</b>
<b>- sound!</b>

02:35.322 --> 02:36.623
<b>- You're ruining the picture!</b>

02:36.623 --> 02:38.592
<b>Maybe you should take off</b>
<b>that gross hat!</b>

02:38.592 --> 02:41.094
<b>- Maybe you should take off</b>
<b>that gross face!</b>

02:41.094 --> 02:43.263
<b>[indistinct arguing]</b>

02:43.263 --> 02:47.000
<b>- Lily! Where is your diaper?</b>

02:47.000 --> 02:49.403
<b>Guys, please!</b>
<b>Can we all just settle down?</b>

02:49.403 --> 02:51.004
<b>[camera shutter clicks]</b>

02:51.004 --> 02:54.308
<b>- Look at us, we're like</b>
<b>a vision of insanity.</b>

02:54.308 --> 02:56.276
<b>I can't give this to</b>
<b>Mom and Dad.</b>

02:56.276 --> 02:57.544
<b>It's worse than Aunt Shirley.</b>

02:57.544 --> 02:59.746
<b>Argh! I mean, my coffee mug!</b>

02:59.746 --> 03:01.582
<b>I've got to give them</b>
<b>a better picture.</b>

03:01.582 --> 03:06.086
<b>The perfect picture.</b>
<b>Time for a do-over.</b>

03:06.086 --> 03:09.890
<b>- Mirror, mirror in my hand.</b>
<b>Who's the prettiest in the land?</b>

03:09.890 --> 03:12.759
<b>- Not you, once Mudzilla</b>
<b>gets a hold of you!</b>

03:12.759 --> 03:13.894
<b>[growls]</b>

03:13.894 --> 03:15.863
<b>- Aah!</b>

03:15.863 --> 03:16.830
<b>- [coughs]</b>

03:16.830 --> 03:19.366
<b>Hey!</b>
<b>You washed off my mud!</b>

03:19.366 --> 03:22.269
<b>Ha ha! You got spray--</b>

03:22.269 --> 03:23.637
<b>- Perfect!</b>

03:23.637 --> 03:25.672
<b>- Hey!</b>
<b>You washed off my makeup!</b>

03:25.672 --> 03:28.375
<b>- Good news, guys. We're taking</b>
<b>another family picture.</b>

03:28.375 --> 03:30.577
<b>both: But we already did one!</b>

03:30.577 --> 03:34.715
<b>- Stay right here.</b>
<b>And no more mud or makeup.</b>

03:34.715 --> 03:35.816
<b>both: What?</b>

03:35.816 --> 03:38.185
<b>- Thank you</b>
<b>for understanding!</b>

03:38.185 --> 03:40.721
<b>Look, I'm all about</b>
<b>self-expression,</b>

03:40.721 --> 03:43.390
<b>but this new picture</b>
<b>needs to be perfect,</b>

03:43.390 --> 03:46.159
<b>so I'm gonna need you</b>
<b>to keep your diaper on.</b>

03:46.159 --> 03:47.561
<b>- [giggles and babbles]</b>

03:47.561 --> 03:50.464
<b>- Thanks for understanding.</b>

03:50.464 --> 03:52.599
<b>- Poo-poo!</b>
<b>[babbles]</b>

03:52.599 --> 03:55.102
<b>- Let's just put a pin in this</b>
<b>for now.</b>

03:55.102 --> 03:57.938
<b>- If the hypotenuse of</b>
<b>a right triangle is</b>

03:57.938 --> 03:59.940
<b>the mean proportional</b>
<b>between segments, then--</b>

03:59.940 --> 04:02.609
<b>- Hey, Lisa, we're doing</b>
<b>another family picture.</b>

04:02.609 --> 04:06.346
<b>How about we lose the glasses</b>
<b>and do something with your hair?</b>

04:06.346 --> 04:07.848
<b> <i>[kazoo blurts]</i> </b>

04:07.848 --> 04:09.082
<b> <i>[off-key guitar chord]</i> </b>

04:09.082 --> 04:10.417
<b> <i>[horn blows]</i> </b>

04:10.417 --> 04:11.418
<b> <i>[bell dings]</i> </b>

04:11.418 --> 04:13.320
<b>- Or just lose the glasses.</b>

04:13.320 --> 04:16.055
<b>- But, Lincoln,</b>
<b>my astigmatism.</b>

04:16.055 --> 04:17.156
<b>[crash, thudding]</b>

04:17.156 --> 04:18.825
<b>- [groans]</b>
<b>- [glass shatters]</b>

04:18.825 --> 04:21.661
<b>- It's okay!</b>
<b>It's just a hairline fracture.</b>

04:21.661 --> 04:25.065
<b>- Did I hear we're taking</b>
<b>more photos? Yay!</b>

04:25.065 --> 04:29.336
<b>Uh-oh. Guess we'll have to wait</b>
<b>till after this solar eclipse.</b>

04:31.205 --> 04:33.307
<b>Whoa. You're like a wizard...</b>

04:33.307 --> 04:36.443
<b>or a weatherman.</b>

04:38.078 --> 04:40.981
<b>- Maybe you should wear these</b>
<b>for the picture, Leni.</b>

04:40.981 --> 04:42.850
<b>They make you look, umm,</b>

04:42.850 --> 04:45.252
<b>even smarter than</b>
<b>you already are.</b>

04:45.252 --> 04:47.254
<b>- Wow! Thanks!</b>

04:47.254 --> 04:48.655
<b>Aah!</b>

04:48.655 --> 04:49.790
<b>[groans]</b>

04:49.790 --> 04:51.525
<b>I'm all right!</b>
<b>I landed on Lisa!</b>

04:51.525 --> 04:54.094
<b>- Okay, now it's a break.</b>

04:54.094 --> 04:56.396
<b>- Okay, just stay here!</b>

04:56.396 --> 04:58.131
<b>- But--</b>

04:58.131 --> 05:01.201
<b>- Here's some ice packs!</b>
<b>And a bandage!</b>

05:01.201 --> 05:04.104
<b>together: Okay, throw them!</b>

05:04.104 --> 05:06.640
<b>- Okay, guys.</b>
<b>Time to take a new picture.</b>

05:06.640 --> 05:09.643
<b>- A new picture? No way.</b>

05:09.643 --> 05:12.045
<b>- Ya ready, Lynn?</b>
<b>Fetch, girl!</b>

05:12.045 --> 05:13.580
<b>- [panting]</b>

05:18.519 --> 05:20.187
<b>- Good, Lynn!</b>

05:20.187 --> 05:21.388
<b>Now stay!</b>

05:21.388 --> 05:24.391
<b>[upbeat music]</b>

05:24.391 --> 05:28.428
<b>♪</b>

05:28.428 --> 05:31.732
<b>- When did we get grass</b>
<b>in our bedroom?</b>

05:31.732 --> 05:33.300
<b>- Time to take a new picture.</b>

05:33.300 --> 05:35.402
<b>- Sweet!</b>
<b>Let me just grab my axe.</b>

05:35.402 --> 05:37.437
<b>- And I'll get my funny nose</b>
<b>and glasses.</b>

05:37.437 --> 05:40.774
<b>- Dudes! Where's my axe?</b>

05:40.774 --> 05:42.442
<b>- And where are my glasses?</b>

05:42.442 --> 05:46.180
<b>- Uh, silly props are not</b>
<b>going to be in this picture.</b>

05:46.180 --> 05:49.116
<b>You'll get them back</b>
<b>after we get the shot.</b>

05:49.116 --> 05:50.517
<b>- You took our stuff?</b>

05:50.517 --> 05:52.186
<b>- Then we're not gonna be</b>
<b>in your picture!</b>

05:52.186 --> 05:54.454
<b>- Hmm.</b>
<b>Sure would be a shame</b>

05:54.454 --> 05:57.658
<b>if something happened</b>
<b>to your things.</b>

05:59.459 --> 06:02.296
<b>- This picture thing has</b>
<b>changed you, dude.</b>

06:02.296 --> 06:05.199
<b>- Which is exactly why</b>
<b>I'm not going to be in it.</b>

06:05.199 --> 06:09.203
<b>- Which is exactly why I took</b>
<b>the liberty of replacing you.</b>

06:09.203 --> 06:10.304
<b>- You what?</b>

06:10.304 --> 06:12.306
<b>[doorbell rings]</b>

06:12.306 --> 06:15.909
<b>- Oh, Lori, I believe you know</b>
<b>Carol Pingrey.</b>

06:15.909 --> 06:19.646
<b>Didn't she beat you out for</b>
<b>homecoming queen?</b>

06:19.646 --> 06:21.715
<b>- Let's get this over with.</b>

06:21.715 --> 06:25.552
<b>- Okay, everyone excited?</b>
<b>So am I!</b>

06:25.552 --> 06:29.156
<b>Ah! There you are!</b>

06:29.156 --> 06:31.625
<b>You aren't getting</b>
<b>that diaper off now!</b>

06:31.625 --> 06:35.062
<b>Okay, pets, move on in!</b>

06:35.062 --> 06:38.532
<b>Okay! Almost there,</b>
<b>just a few more fixes.</b>

