<b>Open up!</b>

06:42.936 --> 06:45.239
<b>You, too.</b>

06:45.239 --> 06:48.442
<b>together: You look thilly.</b>

06:48.442 --> 06:50.177
<b>- Okay, give it here, girl.</b>

06:50.177 --> 06:53.814
<b>- [growls]</b>

06:53.814 --> 06:54.982
<b>- What?</b>

06:54.982 --> 06:56.149
<b>- That hair.</b>

06:56.149 --> 06:58.552
<b>- What about it?</b>

06:58.552 --> 07:01.221
<b>But this hair</b>
<b>isn't me, dude!</b>

07:01.221 --> 07:03.690
<b>- And this glasses isn't I,</b>
<b>either!</b>

07:03.690 --> 07:06.193
<b>- Trust me!</b>
<b>You guys look great!</b>

07:06.193 --> 07:09.396
<b>- Okay, Lucy.</b>
<b>I'm gonna need you to smile.</b>

07:09.396 --> 07:11.031
<b>- I can't see that happening.</b>

07:11.031 --> 07:13.433
<b>- I can't see anything</b>
<b>happening!</b>

07:13.433 --> 07:16.603
<b>- Ya know, some folks think</b>
<b>taking someone's picture</b>

07:16.603 --> 07:19.039
<b>actually steals their soul.</b>

07:19.039 --> 07:19.940
<b>- Oh?</b>

07:19.940 --> 07:21.542
<b>- Yeah! Just think of it.</b>

07:21.542 --> 07:24.044
