<b>Hmm, still needs something</b>
<b>to pull it all together.</b>

07:35.255 --> 07:36.657
<b>I know!</b>

07:36.657 --> 07:39.660
<b>Now this is a perfect picture.</b>

07:39.660 --> 07:41.595
<b>- What was wrong with</b>
<b>the other one?</b>

07:41.595 --> 07:44.531
<b>- Oh, well, uh,</b>
<b>it was kind of...</b>

07:44.531 --> 07:45.933
<b>You guys were a little, uh...</b>

07:45.933 --> 07:48.135
<b>- A little what, Lincoln?</b>

07:48.135 --> 07:50.437
<b>- Yourselves?</b>

07:50.437 --> 07:54.708
<b>all: [grumbling]</b>

07:54.708 --> 07:57.144
<b>- So that's what this</b>
<b>is all about.</b>

07:57.144 --> 07:59.313
<b>You don't like us</b>
<b>the way we are.</b>

07:59.313 --> 08:02.382
