08:07.187 --> 08:11.491
<b>because heaven forbid we be</b>
<b>our actual, literal selves!</b>

08:11.491 --> 08:12.893
<b>together: Cheese.</b>
<b>- Lori,</b>

08:12.893 --> 08:14.862
<b>I didn't mean--uh, um...</b>

08:14.862 --> 08:17.497
<b>Actually,</b>
<b>that's pretty perfect.</b>

08:17.497 --> 08:19.032
<b>[camera shutter clicks]</b>

08:19.032 --> 08:21.034
<b>- Thanks so much, guys!</b>
<b>I really appreciate your--</b>

08:21.034 --> 08:22.936
<b>Guys? Guys? Huh.</b>

08:22.936 --> 08:25.239
<b>Guess they must've had</b>
<b>something else to do.</b>

08:25.239 --> 08:29.576
<b>My days of giving lame</b>
<b>anniversary presents are over.</b>

08:33.413 --> 08:35.515
<b>Mom and Dad are gonna love this!</b>

08:35.515 --> 08:38.452
<b>Look at us. We're like</b>
<b>a vision of perfection.</b>

08:38.452 --> 08:42.688
<b>- Mirror, mirror in my hand.</b>
<b>Who's the prettiest in the land?</b>

08:42.688 --> 08:45.225
<b>- Not you, after</b>
<b>the mud monster gets you!</b>

08:45.225 --> 08:48.061
<b>- [screams]</b>
<b>- Roar!</b>

08:48.061 --> 08:49.730
<b>- Aah!</b>
<b>- Come back here!</b>

08:49.730 --> 08:51.298
<b>- [screaming]</b>

08:51.298 --> 08:54.601
<b>- [roaring]</b>

