<b>the real you,</b>

10:23.490 --> 10:25.259
<b>the perfect you.</b>

10:25.259 --> 10:28.662
<b>together:</b>
<b>Aww, thank you, Lincoln!</b>

10:28.662 --> 10:31.031
<b>- By the way,</b>
<b>you all might wanna put</b>

10:31.031 --> 10:33.400
